---

<DocsLayout
  title="API Reference"
  description="v0.1 public API reference for the implemented Q1 surface, with reserved Q2/Q3/Q4 contracts marked separately."
  active="api"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="status-strip">
      <span>Source: docs/api.md</span>
      <span>Q1 vertical slice</span>
      <span>Reserved contracts labelled</span>
      <span>React consumer surface</span>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">
      Import components and React-aware types from <code>@bc-grid/react</code>. Import
      framework-agnostic contracts from <code>@bc-grid/core</code> when a non-React package needs
